    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-80b6-9c0a-e85677c5776b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper makes a comparison between the Self-Regulated Learning traits exhibited by graduate versus undergraduate students, specifically when it comes to motivational beliefs, deep processing strategies and motivational engagement.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-80b6-9c0a-e85677c5776b",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "18c4750c-f3ba-8037-9662-ccfd37d9f5fe"
        },
        "created_time": "2025-02-01T19:49:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2025-02-01T19:50:00.000Z",
        "created_by": {
          "object": "user",
          "id": "20a7795c-3622-4527-bd13-5ddbf48dc31d"
        },
        "last_edited_by": {
          "object": "user",
          "id": "20a7795c-3622-4527-bd13-5ddbf48dc31d"
        },
        "has_children": false,
        "in_trash": false,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "paragraph": {
          "rich_text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "The paper makes a comparison between the Self-Regulated Learning traits exhibited by graduate versus undergraduate students, specifically when it comes to motivational beliefs, deep processing strategies and motivational engagement.",
                "link": null
              },
              "annotations": {
                "bold": false,
                "italic": false,
                "strikethrough": false,
                "underline": false,
                "code": false,
                "color": "default"
              },
              "plain_text": "The paper makes a comparison between the Self-Regulated Learning traits exhibited by graduate versus undergraduate students, specifically when it comes to motivational beliefs, deep processing strategies and motivational engagement.",
              "href": null
            }
          ],
          "icon": null,
          "color": "default"
        },
        "archived": false
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-800c-8166-e63428b8aa27",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that graduates tend procrastinate less and have better developed critical thinking skills. Conversely, undergraduates assign more-value to specific tasks and are more motivated to enroll in more online courses. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18d4750c-f3ba-800c-8166-e63428b8aa27",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "18c4750c-f3ba-8037-9662-ccfd37d9f5fe"
        },
        "created_time": "2025-02-01T19:50:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2025-02-01T19:52:00.000Z",
