        "type": "paragraph",
        "paragraph": {
          "rich_text": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": {
                "content": "Results show that graduates tend procrastinate less and have better developed critical thinking skills. Conversely, undergraduates assign more-value to specific tasks and are more motivated to enroll in more online courses. ",
